description: During a walk in the lost city of Marchimont, Suske discovers a thousand year old ring. It possesses magical powers and Suske becomes the Chosen One. He has to save the citizens of Marchimont from the evil forest spirit Clamora, but that won't be easy: the spirit of Clamora can take possession of others. Thus Suske faces unexpected opponents and must make heartbreaking choices.
name: Het Gebroken Dorp

description: School is in session -- but your school was never like this! Join Sabrina the Teenage Witch on a magical journey to witch school, where all magical secrets are kept. Brush up on your potions, get a taste of transmutations, and learn how to fly on your magic broom! This textbook-sized digital exclusive has over 150 pages of spells and stories for you to enjoy.

When a high-ranking official of a small nation in the Caucasus is killed in a car accident, the plans of a massive multinational corporation are derailed by one man: the unfortunate French trucker who caused the accident. Pressure from the unions in France and the military in Khalakjistan prevents a quick diplomatic solution. So, to secure its own interests, the corporation calls upon the one man who can break the trucker out of prison and disarm the confrontation: Wayne Shelton.
name: De Missie
